üîó Communication Links

Client System ‚Üí Application Server

Protocol: HTTP / HTTPS

Purpose: User interaction and requests

Application Server ‚Üí Prediction Engine Server

Protocol: API / Service call

Purpose: Demand forecasting

Application Server ‚Üí Database Server

Protocol: SQL / JDBC / ORM

Purpose: Data storage and retrieval

Prediction Engine Server ‚Üí Database Server

Protocol: SQL

Purpose: Access historical sales data
